Name: Strike VR
About the game: A shooter arcade game.. except you survive by moving your head to dodge bullets, enemies, and obstacles. You have two weapons: one on each arm. Can you beat the last boss? Features - 3 different unique stages with 5 levels each - Total of 16 levels - Endless Mode - 11 unique bosses - Weapons: Guns & Swords - 3 different types of abilities - 5 different types of ultimates - Over 15 types of unique enemies Developed by one person..
